HOW TO INSTALL
--------------

To install this package, unzip and untar the file, then build the 
makefile and use make or nmake to install:

    tar xzf Config-LotusNotes-x.xx.tar.gz
    cd Config-LotusNotes-x.xx
    perl Makefile.PL
    nmake
    nmake test
    nmake install


This package also contains an ActiveState PPM package. 
To install it, run the following command in the current directory:

    ppm install Config-LotusNotes.ppd
